      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/464df75643b85d808ea7457d333c2520_1608321291669278925.png",
                "id": "talent34815",
                "key": "Hurtling Bolts",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hurtling Bolts"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Cicin</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/ba8a520b631a5349ea54ca1fad2ec264_2455359249914028842.png",
                "id": "talent20537",
                "key": "Misty Call",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Misty Call"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>, applies <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro Application</span> to this character, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Cicin Shield</span> and prepares <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Surging Thunder</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Electro Cicin Shield</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span><br>Provides <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1 Shield point</span> for your active character.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When created:</span> If you have <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Cicin</span> on the field, additionally increase <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield</span> by the amount of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> it has. (Adds a maximum of 3 additional <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield</span>)<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Surging Thunder</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span><br>(Prepare for 1 turn)<br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/58e7aa03ca09a144cdac07649148383f_1296984294617487401.png",
                "id": "talent31877",
                "key": "Thundering Shield",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Thundering Shield"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 3</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After your opponent plays a total of 3 Action Cards:</span> This card gains 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span>. (Max 3 stacks)<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After Fatui Electro Cicin Mage takes Elemental Reaction DMG:</span> This card loses 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_785237539469174729.png",
                "id": "talent49039",
                "key": "Electro Cicin",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/c32e8d1f898b13385973738aba9d5c6a_3481298486046003884.png",
                "title": "Electro Cicin"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_3926319997056385729.png",
                "id": "talent57666",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Shield</span></strong><br>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro Application</span></strong><br>When Electro is applied without dealing any DMG, the Elemental Reactions triggered will ignore DMG-dealing effects:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: The target is forcibly switched to the next character<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: No effect<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: No effect<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: Creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_9100453268012717540.png",
